{"tid":164745,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭忽撐港足　英雄輝轉身走","createTime":"2017-03-21T01:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T05:31:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6f247c9d5f6639527c317867e4f26344b6b491","tid":164745,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19965231&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19965231%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170321&d=bDN9RnBWsu2ZFehd%2BUm4uOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=b01031a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19965231%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170321&h=a786e674\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19965231&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170321</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭忽撐港足　英雄輝轉身走<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港足球代表隊昨晨在港會足球場開操，為2019亞洲盃外圍賽首輪賽事作客黎巴嫩做準備，林鄭月娥突到場「撐港隊」，又預祝港隊成功，卻遭港隊隊長葉鴻輝冷待，全程與林鄭零交流。「英雄輝」事後稱：「我哋想要實質嘅支持&hellip;&hellip;唔好淨係過嚟講幾句加油就算。」<br />\n<br />\n港隊在2018世界盃外圍賽出局，但球隊在外圍賽表現出色，獲球迷及市民支持，與林鄭爭逐特首寶座的曾俊華更是少數曾現場支持港足的高官。林鄭日前則主動聯絡足總希望與港隊見面，獲安排於昨晨到訪與球員傾談。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨行近欲與葉鴻輝交談，葉即轉身入球場準備操練。伍家亮攝<br />\n<br />\n「唔好淨係講幾句加油」<br />\n<br />\n林鄭向港隊年輕球員講話時表示，與足總主席梁孔德合作促成興建將軍澳足球訓練中心，將來會投放更多資源在足球；林鄭「撐」港隊全程不足30分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n港隊隊長葉鴻輝在林鄭撐場時，全程坐在地上接受物理治療師包紮，到林鄭行近葉身旁，葉即時轉身入球場準備操練。<br />\n<br />\n葉其後承認與林鄭無任何交流，對於林鄭稱認識其名字，並似主動找他傾偈，英雄輝不以為然稱︰「係咩？我唔知道。可能我啱啱同物理治療師講嘢，腳受咗傷、只顧做物理治療而冇睇到其他事。」<br />\n<br />\n他不諱言︰「我哋要嘅係實質支持，唔只係到場。其實港隊需要嘅係球場，唔係只話香港隊，整個香港足球圈都需要球場，希望港府建造更多球場，唔好淨係過嚟講幾句加油就算。」<br />\n■記者曾雁平"},{"pid":"b97a9aa63b65c981c6edd24e84421beea70107df","tid":164745,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"林鄭昨行近欲與葉鴻輝交談，葉即轉身入球場準備操練。伍家亮攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170321/large/21la1p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170321%2Flarge%2F21la1p2.jpg&h=06cdc853&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7aec2e4400f04c0d678fd8ce4bbd578fe7343d3b","tid":164745,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:43:32.000Z","msg":"唔識大體<br />\n我鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41d9b6244e59793b3b2529fae61bf03106d69abb","tid":164745,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:45:12.000Z","msg":"Ho ball<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6594b0bcc23f018ca11bb6d862d5f6abddeee5b8","tid":164745,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:46:38.000Z","msg":"佢有冇俾足總照肺?"},{"pid":"014746bb665d7c07a479eea1d3fbb61cffd7e079","tid":164745,"uid":3109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"我都唔明，淋病訓係到都贏做乜仲要搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e49fdaafeacc712af0a764477c638230bab0661","tid":164745,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:52:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔明，淋病訓係到都贏做乜仲要搞咁多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要做多啲show先呃到啲港豬同廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdd68a13e5d9ada3a9eaf07c24e8249b7d32184","tid":164745,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T01:56:22.000Z","msg":"問佢知唔知乜野係越位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0f5e32491c4fcc41ec8a1e5d1f1b1ad1853a0c","tid":164745,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime